hint.en:
Uses JSON.parse to evaluate the filter argument.

The JSON representation of this filter configuration looks like this:

{
  "and": [
    {
      "property": "Done",
      "checkbox": {
        "equals": true
      }
    },
    {
      "or": [
        {
          "property": "Tags",
          "contains": "A"
        },
        {
          "property": "Tags",
          "contains": "B"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}

For all possible options see the link below.

https://developers.notion.com/reference/post-database-query-filter
